description.en: DeVault is a community governed and driven digital economy designed around the end user. DeVault offers a custom Cold Rewards system for long-term hodlers akin to a Mileage program as well as lets 100% of users participate in governance and cold rewards, no masternodes, no ICO. Just a Proof of Work driven community economy.
